{"talk":{"id":26779,"name":"Mara Mintzer: How kids can help design cities","description":"Adults tend to think of kids as \"future citizens\" -- their ideas and opinions will matter someday, just not today. But kids make up a quarter of the population, so shouldn't they have a say in what the world they'll inherit will look like? Urban planner Mara Mintzer shares what happened when she and her team asked kids to help design a park in Boulder, Colorado -- and how it revealed an important blind spot in how we construct the built environment. \"If we aren't including children in our planning, who else aren't we including?\" Mintzer asks.","slug":"mara_mintzer_how_kids_can_help_design_cities","recorded_at":"2017-11-11 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-11-07 21:00:57","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:46:15","viewed_count":1285439,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":444,"name":"TEDxMileHigh"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6bdddcbf36ee9f9c30c8231ba8bc3b891523758d_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6bdddcbf36ee9f9c30c8231ba8bc3b891523758d_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6bdddcbf36ee9f9c30c8231ba8bc3b891523758d_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/6bdddcbf36ee9f9c30c8231ba8bc3b891523758d_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/573d848f61d21239b406b31aabe4acf47a2518c5_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaraMintzer_2017X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7197409,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaraMintzer_2017X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":19906341,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaraMintzer_2017X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde